doi:10.1111/j.1740-1461.2011.01230.x</li>

<li>Randall, Janet and Lawrence Solan, 2025, &ldquo;Legal Ambiguities:
What Can Psycholinguistics Tell Us?&rdquo;, in
 <a href="#Tobia2025">Tobia 2025</a>,&nbsp;578&ndash;609.</li>
 
<li>Raz, Joseph, 1970 [1980], <em>The Concept of a Legal System: An
Introduction to the Theory of Legal System</em>, Oxford: Clarendon
Press. Second edition 1980.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1975 [1990], <em>Practical Reason and Norms
(Hutchinson University Library)</em>, London: Hutchinson. Second
