York: Oxford University Press.
doi:10.1093/acprof:oso/9780199562688.001.0001</li>

<li>Rehren, Paul and Valerij Zisman, 2022, &ldquo;Testing the
Intuitive Retributivism Dual Process Model&rdquo;, <em>Zeitschrift
f&uuml;r Psychologie</em>, 230(2): 152&ndash;163.
doi:10.1027/2151-2604/a000461</li>

<li>Robbennolt, Jennifer K., 2000, &ldquo;Outcome Severity and
